{"data":[{"date":"23:11 14/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Osmar trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \u201c\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a m\u01b0a \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai cho hay: \"Sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p\u00a0Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 em ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i k\u00e9o Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai nh\u01b0ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khen ng\u1ee3i. HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh\u00a0n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, em l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. Ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n gi\u00fap kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Ninh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng qua 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00f4i, n\u00f3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd th\u00ec tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, d\u1ec5 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn chi\u1ec1u nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5, ch\u1ea1y nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, HAGL s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p SLNA. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tinh th\u1ea7n cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Vinh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng khen h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung h\u01a1n song \u00f4ng v\u1eabn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu m\u00e0 \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\">HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00f3t tim</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4228","checkdouble":"191193"},{"date":"22:26 14/07","title":"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/17/hlv-can-tho-che-kheo-cau-thu-hagl-nam-san-qua-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e2u gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u 14/7.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/hlv-can-tho-che-kheo-cau-thu-hagl-nam-san-qua-nhieu.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/7, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Osmar Moreira v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh. Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch cho hay: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i s\u1eadp b\u1eaby \u1edf hai b\u00e0n thua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp gh\u00e9p. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u00f4m nay c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9n \u0111au\u00a0thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi Patiyo v\u00e0 T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u1edf n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cM\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HAGL. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi thua, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 thua b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 hai trong hi\u1ec7p 2\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 khi V-League 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \"Chi\u1ec1u nay S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 thua Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\", HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4227","checkdouble":"191195"},{"date":"19:53 14/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/nongs-hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea, Brian Laudrup th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chia tay CLB Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n sang Real Madrid</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00d3NG Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00d3NG Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/NONG-Eden-Hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n sang Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi CLB Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o hai n\u0103m n\u1eefa. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Hazard \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chia tay The Blues v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 sau m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Brian Laudrup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch cho r\u1eb1ng Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Eden Hazard v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0Eden \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid\u00a0v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t cho c\u1ea3 anh \u1ea5y l\u1eabn Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n anh \u1ea5y trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ecdi m\u1ed9t, v\u00ec Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard n\u0103m nay 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng vinh quang trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Real \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Ronaldo, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho Eden Hazard. V\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai sau khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/_102527296_jorginho_getty2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/NONG-Eden-Hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/che.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\">Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Sarri, v\u00e0 Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4226","checkdouble":"191182"},{"date":"19:41 14/07","title":"Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal: Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/boreham-wood-vs-arsenal-giao-huu-clb-hom-nay.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \"nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u\" t\u1edbi t\u1eeb h\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. Trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t hattrick.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Do l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e8 2018, l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Arsenal ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy t\u1ee5 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf Nga (do \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i) th\u00ec v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam, ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi Unai Emery, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf Arsene Wenger v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u1ec7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/14/Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qua, Petr Cech. \u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Bellerin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 1 CLB trong khi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Aubameyang vs Lacazette. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Sokratis Papastathopoulos, trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n t\u1eeb Dortmund v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro. S\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1eebng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League nh\u01b0 Maitland-Niles, Willock hay Nelson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Qu\u00e2n xanh\" \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng: Boreham  Wood, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i Anh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t  \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua xa v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Arsenal d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i  khai cu\u1ed9c d\u00f9 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \"ch\u1eafp v\u00e1\". V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n 6 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau  c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0m ch\u00e1y g\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Aubameyang, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o  \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n (ghi 10 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i  Premier League 2017/18).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Boreham Wood vs Arsenal giao h\u1eefu CLB 21h00 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Boreham Wood vs Arsenal giao h\u1eefu CLB 21h00 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Truc-tiep-Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal-giao-huu-CLB-21h00-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aubameyang l\u1eadp hattrick ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 17 ph\u00fat</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 2-0. Maitland-Niles, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Boreham Wood r\u1ed3i  t\u1ea1t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean ngang cho Aubameyang lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh  tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 16, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u0103ng l\u00ean 3 b\u00e0n. Reiss Nelson, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7  sinh n\u0103m 1999 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Wenger s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng  m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Aubameyang nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng  ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 24, ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Arsenal tr\u1edf n\u00ean  h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n sau m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cech, m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i  b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb rung l\u00ean. Ph\u00fat 33, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH Czech  ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ra tay c\u1ee9u nguy cho \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\". Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi  c\u1ee7a Boreham Wood \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 sau \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c h\u00e3m b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ng\u1ef1c r\u1ed3i  vu\u1ed1t m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Nelson t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o do Lacazette th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 40, Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ean l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ecm  ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Aubameyang. 0-5 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, HLV Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Trong danh s\u00e1ch 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 Mustafi,  Mkhitaryan, Ramsey, Chambers, Kolasinac. Ph\u00fat 53, Kolasinac c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb  Nketiah (sinh n\u0103m 1999) b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery da co man khoi dau tung bung o Arsenal\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/4E3E423900000578-0-image-a-71_1531584586775.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong tay c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Boreham Woold c\u1ee9  kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3. Ph\u00fat 66, Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng  b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd do l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 7 \u0111\u00e3  xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. T\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u01a1n 25m, Reine-Adelaide (ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p sinh  n\u0103m 1998) tung ra c\u00fa n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 79, Kolasinac chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng s\u1ec7t v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan, c\u1ef1u  ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man Utd, \u0111\u00e3 b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng t\u1ec9a v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1  b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 8 cho Arsenal \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp  t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 sao, tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V\u00a0Arsenal. Sau \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid vs PSG trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ICC\u00a02018.\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal: </strong>Cech, Bellerin, Sokratis, Mavropanos, Osei-Tutu, Maitland-Niles, Willock, Smith Rowe, Nelson, Aubameyang, Lacazette<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4225","checkdouble":"191183"},{"date":"20:49 14/07","title":"Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a anh kh\u1ecfi M.U trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pogba s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Paul Pogba \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barca, Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n &ldquo;si\u00eau c\u00f2&rdquo; Mino Raiola &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng t\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap Pogba hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Pogba t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2015, Barca t\u1eebng kh\u00e1t khao s\u1edf h\u1eefu Pogba nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juve. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean su\u1ed1t hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, Pogba \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga, Barcelona, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh nh\u01b0 Griezmann hay Umtiti \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Barca, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chia tay c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Pogba, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd hai ng\u00f4i sao mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 PSG Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla, Steven Nzonzi cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\">Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Croatia?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe-469-191061.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe-469-191061.html\">Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh anh c\u00f2n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Mbappe \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 19.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#111000\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4224","checkdouble":"191187"},{"date":"21:36 14/07","title":"Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter Milan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho Croatia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a CLB M.U.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Inter \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Perisic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i hay ph\u1ea3i. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111ang th\u1ecfa lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Perisic t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho anh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen: \u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 nhanh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Nh\u01b0ng Perisic c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe n\u1eefa. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Perisic gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Mandzukic ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe. Perisic th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u00eda M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Inter y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 Perisic \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao t\u1ea1i World Cup m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u2018chi kh\u1ee7ng\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror (Anh) \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Perisic t\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac ngay trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich-421-191168.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich-421-191168.html\">Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu Croatia v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Zlatko Dalic l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\">HLV Croatia n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta \u00edt gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\">Modric: T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#111000\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4223","checkdouble":"191192"},{"date":"01:47 15/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ed1t d\u1ebbo c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau khi Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri, Eden Hazard c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ede Bernabeu, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo sau khi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha k\u1ebft th\u00fac 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Eden Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Eden Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eden Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u, cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-anh-421-191185.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018</span>. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eeba m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Hazard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c anh ch\u1eafc c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.&rdquo; &ndash; Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, Eden Hazard tr\u1ea3i qua 6 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i gi\u00fap anh v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, m\u1ed9t FA Cup, m\u1ed9t League Cup v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Europa League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4222","checkdouble":"191203"},{"date":"14:27 14/07","title":"T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ecda b\u1eaft Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tay-ban-nha-doa-bat-ronaldo-tai-italia.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4221","checkdouble":"191161"},{"date":"14:30 14/07","title":"\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1\" Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/thanh-an-va-neymar-hot-nhat-tren-facebook-tai-anh-mua-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c fan x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 nh\u1eafc t\u00ean Neymar, Messi, C. Ronaldo nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, Lingard...</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Facebook, trong m\u00f9a World Cup 2018, th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Anh nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \"g\u00e2y b\u00e3o\" m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ney-6889-1531537635.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Facebook \u1edf Anh nh\u1eafc t\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Messi, C. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Harry Kane.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Neymar l\u00e0 Messi. Si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Argentina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng khi \"t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\" trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Ireland v\u00e0 Croatia. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh k\u1ecbp to\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Argentina v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 tango v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 ba trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0 C. Ronaldo. Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi Messi, C. Ronaldo to\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 khi ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Mar\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Real l\u1ea1i \"t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\" trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn sau. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Harry Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 trong danh s\u00e1ch. Ba v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec1u\u00a0 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh g\u1ed3m Harry Maguire, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Jordan Henderson. Trong top 10 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ramos, De Gea v\u00e0 Rashford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Facebook \u1edf Anh nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a World Cup 2018<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Neymar<br>\r\n2. Lionel Messi<br>\r\n3. Cristiano Ronaldo<br>\r\n4. Harry Kane<br>\r\n5. Harry Maguire<br>\r\n6. Jesse Lingard<br>\r\n7. Jordan Henderson<br>\r\n8. Sergio Ramos<br>\r\n9. Marcus Rashford<br>\r\n10. David De Gea<br>\r\n11. Luis Suarez<br>\r\n12. Luka Modric</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4220","checkdouble":"191162"},{"date":"14:00 14/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 1-0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (H1): Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hai-phong-vs-binh-duong-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.art