.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP HAGL VS C\u1ea6N TH\u01a0</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4218","checkdouble":"191160"},{"date":"15:42 14/07","title":"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Napoli-muon-mua-Karim-Benzema-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAncelotti \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Benzema lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Ancelotti \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Napoli chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Theo La Sexta, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, n\u1ebfu Benzema c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Napoli, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Napoli c\u00f3 Benzema</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema mo ty so sau sai sot cua Karius\" title=\"Benzema m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau sai s\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Benzema cho Napoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Benzema, Isco, Bale hay Asensio. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Napoli ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Benzema v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4217","checkdouble":"191165"},{"date":"17:04 14/07","title":"Roma b\u00e1o tin vui cho Real v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Roma-ban-Alisson-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Alisson, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Karuis, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma. Vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roma s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianLuca Di Marzio.com kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 45 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Alisson nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea, Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Real ph\u1ea3i \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, Brazil c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 anh v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia c\u00f3 to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4216","checkdouble":"191170"}]}